The paper also discusses the use of robust features, which is a topic relevant to artificial intelligence (AI) research. The paper addresses the issue of adversarial attacks, which is a topic in computer security (CR) research. Finally, the paper proposes a new training method, which is a topic in neural networks (NE) research.
